import { Link } from "react-router-dom"

const Footer = () => {
  
  return (
    <footer>
        <form 
        className="form-control"
        >
           <Link to="/" >
            <input type="submit" value='LogOut'/>
           </Link> 
        </form>
    </footer>
  )
}

export default Footer
